[{"date":"1984-07-25","platform":"剧场版","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/ff/18/77483_cPKPs.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/ff/18/77483_cPKPs.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/ff/18/77483_cPKPs.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/ff/18/77483_cPKPs.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/ff/18/77483_cPKPs.jpg"},"summary":"　　这部短片于1984年7月25日在明尼阿波利斯（明尼苏达州）举行的SIGGRAPH（计算机图形学顶级年度会议）上首映。该片导演在迪斯尼提出提案被开除，而后加入皮克斯的前身。\r\n　　清晨第一束阳光照在大峡谷边缘的树林里，万物重焕生机。树林中央，小铁皮人安德鲁边伸懒腰边打着哈欠，从一夜的美梦中醒来。当他还没来得及看清眼前这片迷人的美景时，一只名叫威利的小蜜蜂飞到他的面前，咄咄逼人，好像要发起攻击。安德鲁吓得浑身发抖，落荒而逃，但威利紧追不放，杀气腾腾。有趣的小故事，意外的结局，为一段伟大而辉煌的历史拉开序幕。 \r\n　　本片为原迪斯尼动画师约翰·拉斯特(John Lasseter)加盟卢卡斯电影公司（皮克斯前身）制作的动画片，也是皮克斯首部短片，系为美国数位图像协会制作，安德鲁人物造型参考了米老鼠。","name":"The Adventures of André and Wally B.","name_cn":"安德烈和威利的冒险","tags":[{"name":"短片","count":40,"total_cont":0},{"name":"欧美","count":25,"total_cont":0},{"name":"pixar","count":21,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1984","count":13,"total_cont":0},{"name":"剧场版","count":10,"total_cont":0},{"name":"美国","count":9,"total_cont":0},{"name":"3D","count":9,"total_cont":0},{"name":"lucasfilm","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"中庸","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"实验动画","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"皮克斯","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1980s","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"80年代","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动画","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"AM","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Pixar.Animation.Studios","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"AlvyRaySmith","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1980-1989","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"原创","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"美漫","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"安德烈和威利的冒险"},{"key":"上映年度","value":"1984年7月25日"},{"key":"片长","value":"1分53秒"},{"key":"官方网站","value":"http://www.pixar.com/shorts/awb/index.html"},{"key":"动画制作","value":"The LUCASFILM COMPUTER GRAPHICS PROJECT"},{"key":"导演","value":"Alvy Ray Smith"},{"key":"话数","value":"1"},{"key":"制